    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/4674caba443f01807c043c1945458735.avif?t=1726618775\" width=610 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >幸存</h2>你必须使用不同的角色类型、武器和宠伴，在不同的外星星球上杀出一条血路，尽力触达最终的Boss并取得胜利。<br>沿途收集宝石以选择新技能并升级你的角色。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/5b1f5620eff9d6c8a92d1dbd0d40549a.poster.avif?t=1726618775\" width=609 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/5b1f5620eff9d6c8a92d1dbd0d40549a.webm?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多个Boss</h2>拼命存活到每个阶段结束，并遇到最终的Boss。<br>游戏中会出现一系列不断变化的技能、力量和能力，玩家必须组合它们的效果才能打倒关末的Boss。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/a175c16e5559eaedddb1aec6c69dee9b.poster.avif?t=1726618775\" width=608 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/a175c16e5559eaedddb1aec6c69dee9b.webm?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/a175c16e5559eaedddb1aec6c69dee9b.mp4?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >终极技能</h2>除了常见的技能外，每个角色都有独特的技能和终极力量。<br>你可以组合技能来创造新的更强大的技能。你能坚持到最后吗？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/434f133f01ce39b0edc9d081461a80ff.poster.avif?t=1726618775\" width=606 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/434f133f01ce39b0edc9d081461a80ff.webm?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/434f133f01ce39b0edc9d081461a80ff.mp4?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>每个角色的独特建模和终极技能<br></li><li>宠物伴侣<br></li><li>自动瞄准或手动瞄准，自由切换<br></li><li>有3张地图和5个角色可供选择。无尽模式即将到来<br></li><li>具有独特行为模式的迷你Boss和关末Boss<br></li><li>简短的25分钟游戏时间</li></ul>",
